    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/542f76aa3c2350e089d956a47a83948f.avif?t=1749464196\" width=625 height=170 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/626cded854ec4e97ed0c904ebe46f9e4.avif?t=1749464196\" width=630 height=121 /></span>探索那些隐藏在黑暗角落里的失落秘密与禁忌力量，踏上穿越地狱神秘之地的征程。在你穿越这些地狱领域时，小心那些危险：地狱的黑暗势力与古老生物已准备好考验你的力量。每一层都隐藏着独特的秘密与挑战，考验你的极限，并奖励那些勇敢揭示隐藏力量的人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/41ce579ea2ac28af98c023508476322b.poster.avif?t=1749464196\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/41ce579ea2ac28af98c023508476322b.webm?t=1749464196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/41ce579ea2ac28af98c023508476322b.mp4?t=1749464196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/fe3f1f18b32c16aca2d19586ac326901.avif?t=1749464196\" width=630 height=121 /></span>作为“Dumbriel”，你将参与快节奏且讲求策略的战斗，这种战斗奖励精准与创造力。凭借庞大的技能和法术库，你可以根据自己的游戏风格塑造“Dumbriel”的旅程。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/a18b2607c77fb494933100082e289efc.poster.avif?t=1749464196\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/a18b2607c77fb494933100082e289efc.webm?t=1749464196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/a18b2607c77fb494933100082e289efc.mp4?t=1749464196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/6870de81c576ed255698523cb2a002a2.avif?t=1749464196\" width=630 height=121 /></span>加入 “Dumbriel” 的地狱深渊之旅，生存仅是开始。当你穿越地狱层层世界时，协助 “Dumbriel” 解开隐藏在每个地狱领域的秘密。遇见NPC盟友，他们将指引你并帮助你踏上自由的征程。一起解开古老谜题，揭开地狱中隐藏的秘密。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/53bd3da81da09541dfcb89a6133dab64.poster.avif?t=1749464196\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/53bd3da81da09541dfcb89a6133dab64.webm?t=1749464196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/53bd3da81da09541dfcb89a6133dab64.mp4?t=1749464196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/8468c4a98989fabcb5321fe4798c921a.avif?t=1749464196\" width=630 height=121 /></span><strong>“Dumbriel”的头目包括：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多阶段战斗</strong>：头目越绝望，战术越变化，战斗难度提升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有目的的个性</strong>：每个头目都不是随机敌人，而是世界观中的关键角色，拥有自己的背景故事。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/9350fbe1b1e61a48b5284c8bd4242a39.poster.avif?t=1749464196\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/9350fbe1b1e61a48b5284c8bd4242a39.webm?t=1749464196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/9350fbe1b1e61a48b5284c8bd4242a39.mp4?t=1749464196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/2beb2c5a55e7e67ce4f42ad4f8556ed0.avif?t=1749464196\" width=630 height=121 /></span>“Dumbriel” 的每个区域都被设计得富有意义并紧密相连，充满丰富的背景故事与等待揭示的秘密。每当获得新技能或物品时，玩家将能解锁原本无法进入的区域，使探索成为游戏的核心体验。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/02680f9c40ff25a84716b8b319a8fcdb.poster.avif?t=1749464196\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/02680f9c40ff25a84716b8b319a8fcdb.webm?t=1749464196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335430/extras/02680f9c40ff25a84716b8b319a8fcdb.mp4?t=1749464196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
